data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN for qualified buyer.  INTEREST RATE less than 3%.  THIS IS IT! The home you've been looking for. This well maintained home is a must see. Hard to find single story, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located on a quiet cul-de-sac. With lovely granite countertops in all wet areas, reverse osmosis, water softener, and a programmable thermostat among the upgrades. You will be the envy of your family and friends with one of the lowest electric bills in the neighborhood, due to the almost hidden solar panels. Relax in the 8ft walk in shower with river rock in the master bath. Read a book in your bay window. Enjoy the giant butterflies hand painted on the back yard fence. Conveniently located to 1604, Lackland AFB and all shopping! This gem won't last long.  Make your appointment today.
